\c 16
\s UHagari loIshmayeli
\p
\v 1 USarayi umkaAbrama wayengamzaleli-ke \add abantwana\x + 15.2,3.\x*\add*; wayelencekukazi umGibhithekazi\x + 12.16; 21.9.\x*, lebizo layo linguHagari\x + Gal. 4.24.\x*.
\v 2 USarayi\x + 20.3,9.\x* wasesithi kuAbrama: Khangela-ke, iN\nd kosi\nd* ingivalile ukuze ngingazali\x + 20.18; 30.2. 1 Sam. 1.5,6.\x*; ake ungene encekukazini yami, mhlawumbe ngingakhiwa ngayo. UAbrama waselalela ilizwi likaSarayi.
\v 3 Ngakho uSarayi umkaAbrama wamthatha uHagari umGibhithe, incekukazi yakhe, ekupheleni kweminyaka elitshumi uAbrama esehlale elizweni leKhanani\x + 12.5.\x*, wasemnika uAbrama indoda yakhe ukuthi abe ngumkakhe.
\v 4 Wasengena kuHagari, wasethatha isisu. Esebonile ukuthi uzithwele, inkosikazi yakhe yasideleleka emehlweni akhe\x + Zaga 30.21,23.\x*.
\v 5 USarayi wasesithi kuAbrama: Ububi bami buphezu kwakho. Mina nginike incekukazi yami esifubeni sakho, ithe isibonile ukuthi izithwele, ngiyadeleleka emehlweni ayo. IN\nd kosi\nd* kayahlulele phakathi kwami lawe\x + 31.53. 1 Sam. 24.12.\x*.
\v 6 UAbrama wasesithi kuSarayi: Khangela, incekukazi yakho isesandleni sakho\x + Jobe 2.6. Jer. 38.5.\x*. Yenza kuyo lokho okuhle emehlweni akho. USarayi waseyiphatha kubi, yasibaleka ebusweni bakhe\x + Eks. 2.15.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasiyifica emthonjeni wamanzi enkangala\x + 20.1. Eks. 15.22. 1 Sam. 15.7.\x*, emthonjeni endleleni eya eShuri\x + 25.18; Eks. 15.22.\x*.
\v 8 Yasisithi: Hagari, ncekukazi kaSarayi, uvela ngaphi, uya ngaphi? Yasisithi: Ngibalekela ubuso bukaSarayi inkosikazi yami.
\v 9 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuyo: Buyela enkosikazini yakho, ubusuzehlisela ngaphansi kwezandla zayo.
\v 10 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kuyo futhi: Ngizakwandisa kakhulu inzalo yakho\x + 17.20; 21.18; 25.12-18.\x* ukuze ingabalwa ngenxa yobunengi.
\v 11 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuyo: Khangela, uzithwele, futhi uzazala indodana, njalo uzayitha ibizo layo\x + 17.19. Mat. 1.21. Luka 1.13,31.\x* \add uthi\add* nguIshmayeli\f + \fk uIshmayeli: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq uNkulunkulu uzakuzwa.\f*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* izwile ukuhlupheka kwakho.
\v 12 Yona-ke izakuba ngumuntu ongubabhemi ongathambanga\x + 21.20.\x*, isandla sayo simelane labo bonke, lesandla sabo bonke simelane layo; izahlala phambi kobuso babafowabo bonke\x + 25.18.\x*.
\v 13 Waseyitha iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakhuluma laye ibizo \add lokuthi\add*: Wena Nkulunkulu wokubona. Ngoba wathi: Lapha lami ngimkhangele yini ongibonayo?
\v 14 Ngakho umthombo wabizwa \add ngokuthi\add* iBeri-Lahayi-Royi\x + 24.62; 25.11.\x*\f + \fk iBeri-Lahayi-Royi: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq umthombo walowo ophilayo engibona.\f*; khangela, uphakathi kweKadeshi\x + Nani 13.26. 14.7; 20.1.\x* leBeredi.
\v 15 UHagari wasemzalela uAbrama indodana; uAbrama wasesitha ibizo lendodana yakhe, uHagari ayizalayo, \add wathi\add* nguIshmayeli\x + 16.11.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo uAbrama wayeleminyaka engamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lesithupha mhla uHagari emzalela uAbrama uIshmayeli.